{"tid":1183933,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係日本開間粥店都好過留係香港","createTime":"2019-06-03T10:03:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T01:49:05.000Z","uid":105822,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f24092e5500ade6e3cb81b06b882d21039ffa6","tid":1183933,"uid":105822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T10:03:12.000Z","msg":"根本係日本開咩都大把人幫襯<br />\n開茶記又得, 開貢茶又得, 開粥店又得<br />\n仲可以開夠10間8間賺大錢<br />\n都唔知仲留係香港做咩<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------<br />\n移民日本開粥店 港夫婦：留港看不到前路<br />\n一對原本是教師的港人夫婦，數年前以經營簽證，到日本東京開設港式粥店，吸引不少日本人光顧，至今擁有數間分店。<br />\n<br />\n他們指選擇移民日本，除了因為日本的居住空間較大，生活較舒適外，亦因為留在香港看不到未來會變好，甚至認為香港政府做事的出發點，並非在香港市民身上；又指作為土生土長香港人，感到香港已經變了很多，擔心「五十年不變」的承諾過後，香港會變成怎樣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%96%8B%E7%B2%A5%E5%BA%97-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6-%E7%95%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E5%89%8D%E8%B7%AF-073855142.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%25B2%25A5%25E5%25BA%2597-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%25A9%25A6-%25E7%2595%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%2589%258D%25E8%25B7%25AF-073855142.html&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOKb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=4943a8c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E9%96%8B%E7%B2%A5%E5%BA%97-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%AB%E5%A9%A6-%E7%95%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E5%89%8D%E8%B7%AF-073855142.html</a>"},{"pid":"18a0ca23ca3cddd52b99aba44b6df1172ac38179","tid":1183933,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T10:11:20.000Z","msg":"首先要考到N1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c7d444f7395e6e0dbca383f1363afcd96a2403","tid":1183933,"uid":105822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T10:12:49.000Z",